title: Fear Unlimited Collection
description:
Fear Unlimited is a Adobe Flash based game Tribute to Devil May Cry, This Package 

Includes Fear Unlimited, Fear Unlimited 2 Issue 1, And Fear Unlimited Arena.

You Can use Joystick Controller to play the Fear Unlimited Collection Via Keyboard 

emulation program Joy2Key. I already setup keys for controller and that can be change

from program. For more information, Help, Guide, Please Read Help file in the end of 

installation.


No internet required to play these games.
